<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-Frontier Insurance raised.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Frontier Insurance raised.</headline>
<text>
<p>--EVEREN Securities Inc said Tuesday it raised its rating on Frontier Insurance Group Inc for the six months to outperform from market performer. Frontier announced a definitive agreement to acquire Lyndon Property Insurance from Mercury Finance Co.</p>
<p>--EVEREN, noting that the acquisition should be additive to Frontier's earnings, said it raised its EPS estimates to $3.58 from $3.28 for 1997 and to $4.46 from $3.91 for 1998.</p>
<p>--Frontier Insurance was up 1 at 46-3/4.</p>
<p>		((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
